  { question: "How much does a doctor visit cost in the Gulf?", answer: "With insurance, copays are typically AED/QAR/SAR 50-150 for GP visits. Without insurance, GP visits cost AED 150-400 in the UAE, QAR 150-350 in Qatar, and SAR 100-300 in Saudi Arabia. Specialist visits are 2-3x more expensive." },
